Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.69,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.70,0:00:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.81,0:00:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.02,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.10,0:01:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.54,0:01:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.85,0:01:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十一话\N[悲伤的卡特尔]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!那里!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是联合的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看来醒来了呢，身体还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是采掘资源用的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.06,0:02:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何会在那种机动战士里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表看来又不是联合的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不可以动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那样继续漂流下去就会死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.88,0:02:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何…要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.81,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是医生，和OZ及联合无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.02,0:02:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不属于任何一方的中立地带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还未向你道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.03,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道能借\N穿梭机的地方吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊，身体这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以让病人离去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎样也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你急于做什么都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那对你的身体无益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.81,0:03:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在最重要是让身心休息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能准备穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能等吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能…我不自量力，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小事一桩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你要休养到那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一言为定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，目标继续加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里欧部队会被抛离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然向B区前进，没有改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙用里欧毕竟追不上吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有报告确认到那是托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么都好，我们不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让拿着武器的机动战士接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出动MD就能马上解决它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些技师有联络来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.17,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型机动战士完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特和麦丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想测试它们的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!能马上投入实战吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁出任另一个驾驶员?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你让我出战，蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了记录完整的数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是技术相当的驾驶员会碍手碍脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我交由你指挥消灭托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.02,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得拜叶特和麦丘留士如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不愧曾设计过钢弹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.76,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小意思\N对我们来说易如反掌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是让那个钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶麦丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要他驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙身为驾驶员的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ应该最清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麦丘留士的自爆装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.74,0:05:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在特洛瓦的拜叶特里控制吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.05,0:05:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我已经照你的吩咐弄妥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦\N如果他有任何可疑举动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以引爆麦丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没那必要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以前在西伯利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾和托尔吉斯战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只会想着决一胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次卫星不会被用作挡箭牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.97,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令战斗中断吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何知道那件事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那点事，OZ的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.97,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查一下马上就会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好他自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身在卫星的我或许已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要感谢他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为全靠他，我才能得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.59,0:06:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦你这个优秀部下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.75,0:06:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错，操纵性和\N钢弹几乎没分别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会怎样和MD战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先潜入敌人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.24,0:07:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己从MD的目标中里除去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.45,0:07:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别胡来，我会把你引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的弱点是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机体的基本性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.82,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人手控制的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.16,0:07:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连机动力和反应速度\N也完全一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题只是血肉之驱的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面对那速度能否应付得来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说，宇宙机雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比MD之流更可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不需要MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部白色家伙由我来收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现目标，先由MD进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙来宇宙有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是MD吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的反应慢了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要转为近身战就有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有两部吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵挡住了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对付这家伙\N也要用近身战吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们在和我的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙敢做这种事的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很少见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没时间陪你们玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点带我走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.97,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你潜入了OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是特洛瓦‧巴顿特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.64,0:10:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该是初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.92,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作为从地球的亲善大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在宇宙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大半是技师和劳动人口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.61,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们忍耐着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比地球恶劣的环境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而他们想进步的那股干劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.74,0:11:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,产生了新的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支援他们的财团就是温拿家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温拿家的现任家主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,移居到自己的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了确保卫星居民的权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直挺身而出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球圈统一联合谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在联合军崩溃了的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也作为附近卫星的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以和平主义为前提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ对抗到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温拿先生，来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.85,0:11:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说卡特尔回来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是多大时的照片呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，要你专程送我来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，别客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有事要来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个不孝子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我还是认为自己是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类光是住在宇宙已经很不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.18,0:12:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无理兼无用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我们才一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球圈统一联合谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以求解决问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.69,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不只乘坐机动战士降落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还制造了攻击卫星的藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.36,0:12:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果无人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战争就不会完结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，完结了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的战争完结了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能有何作为?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为小孩的你能有何作为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当一个继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要遵从父母的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再考虑清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是出色的继承人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊莉亚，连你也维护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.32,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，小孩不一定毫无作为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.96,0:13:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我宝贵的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个有志气的继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸他其实也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.63,0:13:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ谈判已经不能解决问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他认为所有卫星团结起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会仍然有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何不告诉我你是我姐姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.95,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸曾告诉我弟弟\N是钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他很生气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听闻各位姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身在各地的资源卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家全部站在你那边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实爸爸也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一个人离家出走时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.37,0:13:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最担心的是爸爸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.47,0:13:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的确是被联合\N追赶才躲到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，根据温拿家的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平根本不需要机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不理那思想单纯地协助他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以武力解决问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又会产生新的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不明白那一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.71,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的钢弹在这里制成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让它在地球毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教授已经不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了战斗，我要再次制造钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在真的还能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了卫星的大家而战吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.94,0:15:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你一样战斗的\N钢弹驾驶员被捉住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部钢弹被当众毁灭用来示警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而卫星的人看得好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.78,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经无人站在钢弹那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，你今后也能战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并非为了\N别人认同才战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家终有一日一定会明白我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去了沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我变得有点伤感呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.87,0:15:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，姐姐我只是说泄气话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们大家都爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，不要悲伤\N我们的卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，伊莉亚姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你们所讲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将来的发展是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何需要防卫军备?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温拿大人\N我们也明白你的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这里是危险的战略据点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.37,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且市民想亲手确保自身安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看着这些擅自制造的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们联想到\N和平安全等字眼吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有温拿氏你的财力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.39,0:16:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个卫星的开发就没可能完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.43,0:16:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的繁荣是市民努力的成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为今后不再须要独裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我何时独裁过?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我反对OZ介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是为了卫星的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这里真的有独裁者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温拿大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来已经不可以由个人拥有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.02,0:16:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你快点决定\N交出这里的管辖权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了制造武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.73,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了制造杀人工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为何要协助他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反对的声音在增强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们在喊不要独占资源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.89,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温拿家的确拥有很多资源卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们从未独占过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了人们在宇宙的繁荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们豁出一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家应该知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的心改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的周围是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸的周围也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.14,0:17:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们…\N我们只是在做正确的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表决结果，全体一致通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这个资源卫星交由OZ管辖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不准他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这个卫星用来制造武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.15,0:18:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?\N爸爸把卫星切离了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!它在继续加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许会影响到卫星的机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是他的本性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只为了自己的利益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抹杀卫星的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终做出这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以表决了吗?各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.34,0:18:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然全体无异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.47,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保卫卫星的和平与秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们马上采取迅速的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.09,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸!请你停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.22,0:19:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样做毫无作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追兵马上就会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对OZ的侵略袖手旁观吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要再\N驾驶机动战士战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.37,0:19:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武力不能解决问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.77,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!别来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支讨厌的雷射炮\N瞄准着这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.62,0:19:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人!请你快逃走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.52,0:19:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，我在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不是在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗没有终结
